{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752800/extras/Logo_616x300_(Steam_opis).png?t=1572803999\" /><br><br><br>Mysterious Realms is a dungeon crawler RPG game about exploring the realms of mystery. In this game you take control over the team of brave Heroes and embark with them on dangerous missions. Mysterious Realms has a very unique combat system based on the deck with Crystals in five colours.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752800/extras/2_boards_(combat_+_skills).png?t=1572803999\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752800/extras/combat+skill.png?t=1572803999\" /><br>Use Crystals to damage enemies. Attack enemy with Crystal in specific colour to deal even more damage. Played Crystal generates Aura in corresponding colour. Use generated Auras to activate Abilities of your Heroes. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752800/extras/Strona_Steam-sel.png?t=1572803999\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752800/extras/explore.png?t=1572803999\" /><br>Examine mysterious objects, slay deadly enemies, deal with treacherous encounters.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752800/extras/Empower_heroes_board.png?t=1572803999\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752800/extras/Develop.png?t=1572803999\" /><br>Develop your Heroes between missions. Buy new equipment, potions, food. Learn new abilities. Empower Crystals.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752800/extras/zones_board.png?t=1572803999\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/752800/extras/Missions.png?t=1572803999\" /><br>Explore three unique zones and conquer the World of Mystery.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Turn based dungeon crawler with unique combat system<br></li><li> Embark on a dangerous missions, bringing glory and riches<br></li><li> Encounter curious objects, dangerous events and deadly enemies<br></li><li> Use Crystals in five colors to overcome obstacles<br></li><li> Attribute base checks<br></li><li> Equip your heroes with powerful equipment<br></li><li> Gameplay inspired by timeless classics such as: Darkest Dungeon, Puzzle Quest, ADOM and Slay the Spire</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Achievements? Check","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/752800/ecbc197889766c1fa00d065b74baaba415e169a4.jpg"},{"name":"That was close","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/752800/87276a1d5944f0f86b29c8c066e591d0384fb22e.jpg"},{"name":"Golden Citizen","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/752800/b805ffdc5ba8f465a542674cb369668e048edada.jpg"},{"name":"It's getting dangerous","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/752800/b48ad3b2243db5e953dcf5318af34b935d2673bb.jpg"},{"name":"Puzzle adept I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/752800/82dfc66035357d7eeaac2c9d719fe4104dd37df2.jpg"},{"name":"The First Warden","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/752800/df12ad2b04cf2af66b98c05a010039340292a94c.jpg"},{"name":"Elemental Lord","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/752800/21e9efeb7704af3ba9462e99856495a83a9d8fd9.jpg"},{"name":"Grim Reaper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/752800/6e29de2cb186ed9155804ff629eef60451048b2c.jpg"},{"n